<div id="review_3973035663" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3973035663" />
    <a title="Karen Fasimpaur" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/51159026-karen-fasimpaur"><img alt="Karen Fasimpaur" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1452613193p2/51159026.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3973035663?book_show_action=true">May 16, 2021</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Karen Fasimpaur" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Karen Fasimpaur" href="/user/show/51159026-karen-fasimpaur">Karen Fasimpaur</a>
      </span>

          added it




        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3973035663" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2027717840097438955">I greatly respect this author&apos;s approach to sustainable agriculture and was drawn to this book by my own feelings that our local food system is paralyzed by over-regulation. In this book, Salatin gives many examples of how this is the case.<br/><br/>However, this is one of those self-published books that would have greatly benefited from some editing. The author strays into many personal gripes that are not related to local food and that frankly detract from the quality of the book, especially as a tool t</span>
  <span id="freeText2027717840097438955" style="display:none">I greatly respect this author's approach to sustainable agriculture and was drawn to this book by my own feelings that our local food system is paralyzed by over-regulation. In this book, Salatin gives many examples of how this is the case.<br /><br />However, this is one of those self-published books that would have greatly benefited from some editing. The author strays into many personal gripes that are not related to local food and that frankly detract from the quality of the book, especially as a tool to mobilize others toward advocacy for local food. </span>
  <a data-text-id="2027717840097438955" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
