    <div class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/author/list/2623.Joel_Salatin">Books by Joel Salatin</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
